# Architecture Decision Records (ADR)

Transversal decisions live in [docs/adr/](../../docs/adr/). Template: [docs/adr/template.md](../../docs/adr/template.md). Index: [docs/adr/README.md](../../docs/adr/README.md).

**Manual acceptance only:** see [development-process.mdc](development-process.mdc) § Manual acceptance only. The agent **never** sets `Accepted` or `Reopened` without explicit user approval.

